# Reserved per the T6 secrets convention. No secrets are currently extracted
# from gitea/docker-compose.yml — the GITEA__* env vars in the compose stanza
# are non-secret coordination (DOMAIN, ROOT_URL, etc).
#
# Gitea's internal secrets (SECRET_KEY, INTERNAL_TOKEN, JWT_SECRET,
# LFS_JWT_SECRET) are owned by the gitea binary and stored on disk in
# gitea/data/gitea/conf/app.ini, which is gitignored as part of **/data/. Do
# not move those into env/ — gitea generates and rotates them itself.
